494
01:20:09,309 --> 01:20:10,853
Men vi kan såre ham.

495
01:20:13,397 --> 01:20:15,649
-Med den her.
-Vi må gå til politiet.

496
01:20:15,732 --> 01:20:18,819
Der er ingen, der vil tro os.

497
01:20:20,070 --> 01:20:21,572
Jeg finder ham.

498
01:20:26,869 --> 01:20:28,495
Amber. Vent.

499
01:20:31,039 --> 01:20:32,165
Kom.

500
01:20:37,462 --> 01:20:38,922
Hvor skal vi hen?

501
01:20:40,174 --> 01:20:43,468
-Den her står åben.
-Jeg tror, han kommer.

502
01:20:45,220 --> 01:20:48,599
Ind, ind. Der kommer han.

503
01:20:50,058 --> 01:20:52,227
-Herhen?
-Nej, her.

504
01:20:58,400 --> 01:20:59,484
Denne vej.

505
01:21:02,154 --> 01:21:05,365
-Kom.
-Vent.

506
01:21:16,084 --> 01:21:20,172
-Sæt krogen der.
-Okay.

507
01:21:20,297 --> 01:21:21,590
Kom herover.

508
01:21:25,427 --> 01:21:26,845
Vi er der næsten.

509
01:21:27,888 --> 01:21:30,057
Vent til jeg siger til.

510
01:21:38,273 --> 01:21:39,650
Er du klar?

511
01:21:48,116 --> 01:21:49,535
Lance, derovre!

512
01:21:51,161 --> 01:21:52,454
Nej, deroppe.

513
01:21:56,792 --> 01:21:57,918
Nu!

514
01:22:31,159 --> 01:22:32,327
Han er væk.

515
01:22:59,354 --> 01:23:02,524
Amber, vi kan ikke blive her.

516
01:23:03,192 --> 01:23:05,277
Kom, lad os komme af sted.

517
01:23:30,969 --> 01:23:32,095
Nej!

518
01:23:33,514 --> 01:23:35,098
Lance, nej!

519
01:24:50,132 --> 01:24:53,927
